text:
I mentioned this in the other channel too <@U01MW6DANC8>, but I would think about this in terms of priorities – is the cash you will spend (a lot of it) bidding on competitor keywords, cash that you can spend better elsewhere?

If you do decide to do it, still good to send people somewhere that aligns with their intent (so a really solid comparison page is good to have, plus a relevant free trial offer so they can compare). Plus consider retargeting the term rather than straight-up bidding on it. Happy to chat more, feel free to DM :slightly_smiling_face:
